The '''University of Agamar''' was an institute of higher learning on [[Agamar/Legends|Agamar]] with a respected [[Archaeology/Legends#Xenoarchaeology|xenoarchaeology]] department during the early years of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. Dr. [[Anki Pace]] worked at the department; [[Jens (student)|Jens]], [[Vil (student)|Vil]], [[Denna]], and [[Trista Orlanis]] were four of her interns helping her on a dig on [[Bimmiel/Legends|Bimmiel]].

